data.description: Come see this amazing property with two adjacent lots totaling over 5 acres! With no Covenants and Sun River water rights, dream it and you can do it! Montana living at its finest in this 5 bedroom, 3 bath home that includes an office. Get cozy in front of a gas fireplace in the step down living room upstairs, or large family room downstairs. Take advantage of the heated 3 car garage or downstairs mechanical room, both have plenty of room for extra storage or a workshop. Outside, the property is fenced with plenty of room for horses, chickens, and any other animals you could want, as well as room for a fantastic garden. Let's not forget the mobile home pad with its own electric and septic. Don't miss out! Call Cory Jackson at 406-868-2148 or your real estate professional to request a tour!
